FBIS4-46150 "jptot022__l94059" JPRS-TOT-94-022-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 22 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA INDIA Terrorists With `Powerful' Bombs Arrested in Delhi Terrorists With `Powerful' Bombs Arrested in Delhi BK2205121494 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0245 GMT 22 May 94 BK2205121494 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] Delhi Police yesterday arrested two Kashmiri terrorists with two powerful plastic bombs which they planned to plant in the VIP areas. The arrested are believed to be important functionaries of the Hizbul Mojahedin. They had extensive training in Pakistan in assembling bombs.
